Interface BaseHvdcLine2TVSC<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Branch, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, HvdcLine2T, IAclfAdjustment, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HvdcLine2TVSC, HvdcLine2TVSCDyn, HvdcLine2TVSCDynPlus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseHvdcLine2TVSCImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCDynImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCImpl

    public interface BaseHvdcLine2TVSC<TBus extends BaseAclfBus<?,?>>
extends HvdcLine2T
    A representation of the model object 'Base Hvdc Line2 TVSC'. Always assume fromBus(rectifier) -> toBus(invetor)

    The following features are supported:

    • IDc Ka
    • Rec Converter
    • Inv Converter
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getBaseHvdcLine2TVSC()
